<div class="home-title">
	<div class="main-column-wide">

		<div class="wide three-title-col">
			<div class="col-1">
				<h1>Web Designer, <br>Web Developer,<br />Graphic Designer</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="col-2">
				<p>
					I am a senior designer who specializes in both web and print design. My almost two decades of experience inform my approach to my work with a deep foundation of wisdom, paired with an ever curious eye to future developments in the industry.
